01:10:24,390 --> 01:10:27,510
Cursed Crystal Prison!

1249
01:10:37,190 --> 01:10:41,030
K-Kazuma-san, chuyện gì đang diễn ra vậy?

1250
01:10:41,440 --> 01:10:43,450
